{"id": 223767992, "title": "15-year-old girl killed in Mount Trashmore shooting, 18-year-old man in critical condition.", "text": "VIRGINIA BEACH \u2014 Two teenagers were shot \u2014 one fatally \u2014 Saturday night at Mount Trashmore Park. The victims were a 15-year-old girl who died from her injuries, and an 18-year-old male who\u2019s in critical condition, according to police. The incident began with a fight inside the park\u2019s summer carnival area, police said. Off-duty Virginia Beach Sheriff\u2019s deputies working secondary jobs at the event quickly broke up the scuffle, but it later resumed in a nearby parking lot on Edwin Drive, police said. \u201cAt least one individual produced a firearm and fired shots,\u201d according to a release from the department. The first call to 911 was received at about 8:30 p.m., the release said. Both victims were taken to a hospital for treatment. The girl, who has not been identified, was later pronounced dead. \u201cThe increase in youth gun violence that we are experiencing in our community is disturbing and reprehensible,\u201d Police Chief Paul Neudigate said in a statement. \u201cIt is heartbreaking to continue to see young lives being lost and families torn apart by these senseless acts.\u201d Police do not have any suspect information at this time. Anyone with information about the incident is asked to contact the department\u2019s detective bureau at 757-385-4101, or anonymously through Crime Solvers at 1-888-LOCK-U-UP/P3tips.com. The carnival, an annual event at the park, opened Friday evening and is scheduled to continue through June 19. Jane Harper, jane.harper@pilotonline.com", "summary": "The incident began with a fight in the park's summer carnival area that was broken up by law enforcement officers. It was later resumed in a nearby parking lot, where the shots were fired.", "url": "https://www.pilotonline.com/2024/05/26/victim-killed-in-mount-trashmore-shooting-was-15-year-old-girl-male-18-in-critical-condition/", "image": "https://www.pilotonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/TVP-SHOOTING-VB-BT-05262024-02.jpg?w=1024", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-26 16:35:40", "author": "Jane Harper", "authors": ["Jane Harper"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": -0.719}